<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dehradoon Public School | Varanasi</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;}
body{background:#f4f6fa;color:#222;}
header{background:#0A2E6D;color:white;padding:20px 8%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
header h1{font-size:22px;}
nav a{color:white;text-decoration:none;margin-left:20px;font-weight:500;}
.hero{height:90vh;background:linear-gradient(rgba(10,46,109,0.7),rgba(10,46,109,0.7)),url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588072432836-e10032774350') center/cover no-repeat;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center;color:white;padding:20px;}
.hero h2{font-size:42px;margin-bottom:15px;}
.hero p{max-width:600px;margin-bottom:25px;}
.btn{padding:12px 25px;border:none;background:#F4B400;color:#000;font-weight:600;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;}
section{padding:70px 8%;}
.section-title{text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:28px;color:#0A2E6D;}
.features{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:25px;text-align:center;}
.feature-box{background:white;padding:25px;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);}
.academics table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;}
.academics th, .academics td{border:1px solid #ddd;padding:15px;text-align:left;}
form{max-width:600px;margin:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:15px;}
input,select,textarea{padding:12px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:4px;}
footer{background:#0A2E6D;color:white;text-align:center;padding:25px;}
@media(max-width:768px){
.hero h2{font-size:30px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>Dehradoon Public School</h1>
<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#academics">Academics</a>
<a href="#admissions">Admissions</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h2>Empowering Young Minds for a Brighter Tomorrow</h2>
<p>CBSE-affiliated school in Varanasi committed to excellence, discipline, and holistic development.</p>
<a href="#admissions" class="btn">Apply Now</a>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
<p style="text-align:center;max-width:800px;margin:auto;">
Dehradoon Public School, located in Domari Parao, Varanasi, is dedicated to nurturing confident, disciplined, and responsible individuals through quality education and value-based learning.
</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
<div class="features">
<div class="feature-box">CBSE Curriculum</div>
<div class="feature-box">Smart Classrooms</div>
<div class="feature-box">Modern Laboratories</div>
<div class="feature-box">Sports & Co-Curricular Activities</div>
<div class="feature-box">Safe Campus</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="academics" class="academics">
<h2 class="section-title">Academic Structure</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Level</th><th>Focus</th></tr>
<tr><td>Pre-Primary</td><td>Play-based foundational learning</td></tr>
<tr><td>Primary</td><td>Concept clarity & values</td></tr>
<tr><td>Middle</td><td>Skill development & subject depth</td></tr>
<tr><td>Secondary</td><td>Board preparation & career readiness</td></tr>
</table>
</section>

<section id="admissions">
<h2 class="section-title">Online Admission Form</h2>
<form>
<input type="text" placeholder="Student Name" required>
<input type="date" required>
<select required>
<option value="">Class Applying For</option>
<option>Pre-Primary</option>
<option>Primary</option>
<option>Middle</option>
<option>Secondary</option>
</select>
<input type="text" placeholder="Parent Name" required>
<input type="tel" placeholder="Contact Number" required>
<input type="email" placeholder="Email" required>
<textarea placeholder="Address"></textarea>
<button class="btn">Submit Application</button>
</form>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>
<p style="text-align:center;">Domari Parao, Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">Phone: +91-XXXXXXXXXX</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">Email: info@dehradoonpublicschool.com</p>
</section>

<footer>
© 2026 Dehradoon Public School | All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>
